end_gcode.1.4.4:
G4 ; wait
M221 S100 ; reset flow
M900 K0 ; reset LA
{if print_settings_id=~/.*(DETAIL @VERTEX|QUALITY @VERTEX|@0.25 nozzle VertexXL).*/}M907 E538 ; reset extruder motor current{endif}
M104 S0 ; turn off temperature
M140 S0 ; turn off heatbed
M107 ; turn off fan
{if max_layer_z < max_print_height}G1 Z{z_offset+min(max_layer_z+30, max_print_height)}{endif} ; Move print head up
G1 X0 Y200 F3000 ; home X axis
M84 ; disable motors

M115 U3.10.2 ; tell printer latest fw version
M880; check the steel sheet
G90 ; use absolute coordinates
M83 ; extruder relative mode
M104 S170 ; set extruder temp
M140 S[first_layer_bed_temperature] ; set bed temp
M109 S170 ; wait for extruder temp
M190 S[first_layer_bed_temperature] ; wait for bed temp

M109 S{first_layer_temperature[initial_extruder]+extruder_temperature_offset[initial_extruder]} ; wait for extruder temp
G1 Z0.20 F720 ; Go down to Z 0.20mm
